reviewText: I did not receive my 3d glasses

THIS MOVIE WAS NOT AS GOOD AS THE ORIGINAL FROM THE 80'S, BUT IT WAS GOOD. I DID GET 3D GLASSES, I DON'T WATCH 3D MOVIES, I LIKE 2D MOVIES. THE ACTING WAS GOOD, BUT THE KILLER IN THIS ONE DID GREAT. I SAY IF YOU HAVE THE ORIGINAL FROM THE 80'S, DO GET THIS ONE.
